  "text": "Alpha error: 5% Power of study: 90% Minimum difference to detect: The sample was calculated to detect a 50% difference in the rate of canine retraction, which was considered to be clinically meaningful. Population Standard Deviation: 0.3 mm [CITATION_1] .",
